title: Türkiye ready to take lead in Black Sea security, sources say
description: Türkiye is, in principle, ready to take the lead in Black Sea maritime security with other partners as part of post-war security guarantees based on a mutually agreed peace deal, diplomatic sources said on Tuesday.
content:
